for linux users: download and put into /opt/mendeleydesktop/share/mendeleydesktop/citationStyles-1.0
for windows/mac users: locate citationStyles-1.0 and put the file into that folder

Updates:

11-01-12: 
Citations now work with libre-office as follows:

Author (Year) or in case of more than work of the same author consecutively: Author (Year), (Year2)
Author1 & Author2 (Year)
Author1, Author2 et al. (Year) - et al. in italics!

Full Citations now work for:
Journal papers
Books
Book Sections
Websites

11-15-12
style is now valid csl: http://validator.nu/?doc=https%3A%2F%2Fraw.github.com%2Fbdrolshagen%2Fmendeley%2Fmaster%2Fzootaxa.csl&schema=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fcitation-style-language%2Fschema%2Fraw%2Fv1.0.1%2Fcsl.rnc&parser=xml&laxtype=yes
